item.title: Another RuneScape fail
item.dc:creator: @vManlyMan vManlyMan
item.description:
@vManlyMan wrote:

[quote=“reyx7, post:20, topic:426276”][quote author=vManlyMan link=topic=528969.msg3859879#msg3859879 date=1324601033]
You’re really saying “gf fagex” because they didn’t put the levels in the order you would have liked?
[/quote]

You’d be mad if it said rune, adamant, bronze, black, steel, barrows, dragon, iron. Order is a perfectly normal thing to expect.[/quote]

Yes, but those are different. There is different levels for each item. But for the flash factory or whatever it’s called, it’s… I dun confused myself.

What i’m trying to say is, I wouldn’t care if it said “Dharok’s , Ahrim’s, Karil’s, Verac’s”, or backwards because they’re all the same requirement. For the Flash Factory, those are the requirements.

You know what, I give up. I’m not well for Mopar right now. maybe i’ll come edit my post when I’m done feeling st00pid, and say what I’v been trying to for the last 5 minutes.
